  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- my conjecture is obviously that the price for freeing him was that from now on, you work for us. us being, I think the anti-Spanish group of the army, which in Berlin was just headed by [INAUDIBLE] Canaris and probably [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had a great high concentration of royalist-minded conservative officers of my father's type, of which he probably knew some from his days in the army.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's conjecture, again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, then he-- OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What happened with these pounds is that Father converted them to gold, I think on the black market or whatever, banks, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the next thing I knew-- first of all, that after years of poverty, we were suddenly living in wealth again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a lot of money around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I remember Father very proudly one day bringing home two wooden boxes, chocolate boxes by a manufacturer that still exists, called Gerbeaud, in Budapest-- in fact, we have a Gerbeaud box here somewhere, they are [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] 30 by 20 centimeter wooden boxes filled with gold coins that he had-- had acquired as a kickback for the family, which of course made him a very rich man.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He kept these in a hotel safe in Pest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was the Hotel Vadaszkurt, or translated, the-- the hunter's horn, the Hunter's Horn Hotel, where he had a permanent room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that also-- you know, we have to-- all conjecture from a child's viewpoint who really has never been talked to about these things, so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I would-- certainly, Father maintained that room for years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think what had happened in the Aryanization process is that they-- they required him to divorce my wife.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
